name: Greg Shane
description: I consider myself to be an intelligent, elegant man. I am not proud but I have a kind of esteem that I am proud to show. Generally I’m a happy person but lately,for some couple of years.I lost that smile. I am a very sensual person, who loves to touch and be touched. I’m loving, romantic, honest, open minded and straight forward. I enjoy my life but really would like to be able to share my smiles with someone special
